The facilities at Gallagher convention Centre can cater for 2-7000 delegates in your choice of 27 multi-purpose venues. We offer five executive boardrooms, ideal for training groups up to 60 delegates. Boardroom 5 is a dedicated Video Conferencing facility and can accommodate up to 10 guests. At Gallagher Convention Centre we cater for a variety of conferences, we also offer clients the option of a half- day conference package inclusive of lunch. Specially priced and formulated for your convenience our promotional DDP packages are valid for June and July 2018. The special training package is valid until the end of March 2019.For more information on the training packages, contact Gallagher Convention Centre or visit our website.